products.title: Splash Chocolate Brown 89mm Vertical Blind
products.description: Their splash range of fabrics are both beautiful and contemporary. Chocolate brown is a stunning, rich shade. We think this colour works perfectly paired with wooden tones in the home. Their vertical blinds can be manufactured with either white or chrome control chains which ensures you get the desired finish for your room. Also, as their made to measure blinds come with a 5 year guarantee you can rest assured you are investing in a piece that will stand the test of time.

products.title: Splash Taupe Brown 89mm Vertical Blind
products.description: Their splash taupe brown vertical blinds are contemporary and stylish. A moisture-resistant medium mink brown fabric, makes this blind a great addition to a kitchen or bathroom. With a variety of control and stacking options available on their headrails, this blind can be easily tailored to work for any window. At swift direct blinds, with fifty years of blind making experiance, quality comes first.

products.title: Splash Mocha Brown 89mm Vertical Blind
products.description: A family favourite, their splash range comes in a wide variety of colours and blinds. Splash mocha brown is a chic medium brown vertical blind - perfect for adding a stylish, modern finish to your home. This light-filtering, dim-out vertical blind is the perfect choice whether you are refreshing a tired looking window or moving into a new home. As a simple plain fabric, this brown vertical blind is especially great for adding a splash of colour in kitchens, as this fabric is also moisture-resistant.
